<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,1254,1999]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">Head and pronotum creamy white with reddish brown mottling, slightly large sized mottling on pronotum anteriorly. Scutum reddish brown with lateral margins ivory white and lateral spot posteriorly darker; scutellum reddish brown, lateral and apical areas ivory white with dark brown spot on lateral margin between them. Forewings silvery white with brown mottling between veins; median spot formed by rich brown mottling, few spots on anterior margin, one larger lateral spot and posterior corner, dark brown. Legs with bases of setae spotted with dark brown.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="113" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,1254,1999]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">
<emphasis box="[199,373,1470,1495]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">
<collectingCountry box="[199,257,1470,1495]" name="Malta" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">Male</collectingCountry>
genitalia.
</emphasis>
Pygofer longer than its height in lateral view, conically rounded posteriorly with stout setae over posterior half. Valve with broadly rounded corners approximately 
<number box="[955,990,1506,1531]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" value="1.5">1.5</number>
times as wide at base as long medially. Subgenital plates with terminal fingerlike process narrow, 
<number box="[807,856,1542,1567]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" value="0.25">0.25</number>
times as long as total length. Style thrice as long as wide at base, preapical lobe poorly developed with few hairlike setae, apophysis straight, slightly directed laterad. Stem of connective about as long as arms. Aedeagal shafts elongate, tapering gradually over distal 
<number box="[1278,1327,1615,1639]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" value="0.33">0.33</number>
length to slender, dorsally directed apex, twisted in middle, faintly serrated in anterior surface; gonopore on posterior surface near midlength of shafts.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,1254,1999]" box="[199,982,1722,1747]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">
